		<title>飢餓は、政治的な暴力</title>
		<link>https://midori1kwh.de/2016/01/10/7635?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e9%25a3%25a2%25e9%25a4%2593%25e3%2581%25af%25e3%2580%2581%25e6%2594%25bf%25e6%25b2%25bb%25e7%259a%2584%25e3%2581%25aa%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258a%259b</link>
